transcript.text: Welcome to on Print shop.
In this video we will learn about the new feature enhanced in shipping and label generation.
As you can see on the screen we have to go to order listing page.
We have this order shipment button.
Click here.
Now you can search for the order number then click on package configuration.
Here in the next step you will see two types of shipment order wise and product wise.
Here we will see product wise.
In this order we have three different products so we can create shipping package according to us.
So let's create the packages.
After the package is created we have to select all the shipping packages and click on save now in order to generate label check the box.
Here select shipping method from the drop down options.
Then select shipping type.
If we select UPS in the shipping method it will ask for label generation via API.
Enable it.
After this we can update order status from here only by enabling update order status button.
Select status as shipped from the drop down to notify the customer.
Check the box and click on submit.
Once we clicked on submit, we can see label has been downloaded.
Thank you for watching this video.
If you have any query, please drop us an e-mail to support at onprintshop com.
